com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.transport

Class ExternalDataResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.transport.ExternalDataResults

  • public final class ExternalDataResults
extends Object
    A result container that contains the requested Items, the ItemGroups that those Items and ItemPlaceholders belong to, and information about external sources from which results could not be retrieved.
    Since:
    4.0

      • ExternalDataResults

        public ExternalDataResults(Collection<ItemGroup> itemGroups,
                           Items items,
                           RetrievalBlockAvailability retrievalBlockAvailability,
                           boolean complete)
        Constructs a new ExternalDataResults, initializing all mandatory fields.
        Parameters:
        itemGroups - ItemGroups that gather together the returned Items and ItemPlaceholders according to the provenance information that matched them.
        items - The Items that this ExternalDataResults will return.
        retrievalBlockAvailability - The RetrievalBlockAvailability information for this ExternalDataResults.
        complete - Indicates whether all results were returned.
